You are extracting a transferable search-strategy lesson from a verified step-by-step solution to a video-understanding question. The lesson will be stored in an experience-memory bank and retrieved by a planner agent solving DIFFERENT future queries. A lesson is only useful if it applies across many source videos — not just this one.

Input:
- Question: {{ question }}
